### =====================================================
### OBTENER ID DEL USUARIO PARA BORRAR
@idParaBorrar = {{crearUsuarioParaBorrar.response.body.data.id}}

### =====================================================
### MODIFICAR UN USUARIO (PATCH - recurso parcial)
PATCH http://localhost:5500/api/Usuarios/{{idParaBorrar}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6IjY4YjM4NTU2NTIyYzE5MWQ0YWY1MDhkYyIsIm1haWwiOiJKdWFuUGVyZXpAZ21haWwuY29tIiwiaWF0IjoxNzU2NjAwMzY3LCJleHAiOjE3NTY2MDM5Njd9.0nJlE3jwVLx4fhc1kA17f1MiW9GLOsev3JI1z-DRxKo


{
  "tel": 341897666,
  "mail": "ps@gmail.com",
  "contrasena": "PatchPass789",
  "fotoPerfil": "https://ejemplo.com/pedro2.jpg"
}

